              Okay, look, I've already stopped reading this thread. Why? Because I'm watching the show and haven't read the books, and I don't want to see your hypotheticals. Not interested. Which is the whole bloody point in the first place.<br /><br />If you cannot understand how that works, then yes, stay out of the show thread. It's that simple. If you think you're capable of not dragging the books in, for any reason at all, period, end of story, then feel free. There's no magic gate that will stop you. We can't ban posters from threads btw. Not technically possible.<br /><br />There really isn't anything else to say about it.

              

              
              
