              @Starbuck79:<br /><br />You seem to think there were no spoilers at all in the thread in the run up to the moderation. I can spot two. They are minor but they are there. What has happened in both cases is this: Some detail which is left unclear in the show but is clear in the books has been clarified by a book reader. That's still spoileration, because every tiny detail in this story can turn out to be critical.<br /><br />@Xaiax: did you really just post spoilers in a discussion about how best to deal with spoilers? The ironing is delicious.

              

              
              
