 the posts that it attracted.  A big &quot;FUCK YOU&quot; to &quot;manners&quot;.<br /><br />What makes a thread about a fucking TV show so special?  Especially when most people are being very careful already, and some people who don't actually know anything are just <span style="font-style: italic">assuming</span> they're spoiling?  <br /><br />You know what else?  I don't even expect a response that makes sense.

              

              
              
