              XaiaX, you missed the point.<br /><br />What has, or hasn't happened in a future book, IS a spoiler.  You are not helping your case here.  You wrote &quot;X hasn't happened yet in the books.&quot;  THAT is a spoiler and a prime example of something that has no business in the &quot;Show Only&quot; thread or this one.<br /><br />I'm intentionally being vague so as not to repeat your spoiler.  You could have easily provided hypothetical examples to  demonstrate your point. There was no need to bring ANY spoilers, from the show OR the books into this discussion.  You also assume that everyone in THIS thread has seen season 1 &amp; 2 of the show.<br /><br />Until the mods do otherwise, the purpose of the Show Only is to avoid ANY mention/reference/acknowledgement of the books existing is off limits.  Book readers are allowed to post as long as they accept those limitations.  Lets keep the same in this thread as we talk about those rules.

              

              
              
